    <div class="w-container">
      <div class="project-header">Canopy: Responsive Web for Interactive Learning Platform</div><img class="project-image" height="400" src="../images/canopy main.png">
      <div class="project-body" data-ix="button-appears">
        <div class="w-richtext">
          <h2>Project&nbsp;Summary&nbsp;</h2>
          <p>Canopy is an educational platform dedicated to teaching people about trading stocks.</p>
          <h4>Context</h4>
          <p>Responsive mobile website.</p>
          <h4>Goal</h4>
          <p>Canopy currently lacks engagement with its users through their lesson and progress flow. We aim to create a course roadmap and introduce interactive components within lessons.</p>
          <h4>Constraints</h4>
          <p>10-week timeline, confined to limited content with ability to scale.</p>
          <h4>Role</h4>
          <p>Product Designer with 6 other designers.</p>
          <h4>Process</h4>
          <p>Click icons below to skip forward to the perspective sections.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="canopy process w-row">
          <div class="w-col w-col-2 w-col-small-2 w-col-tiny-2">
            <a class="persona process-link-block w-inline-block" href="#persona-development"></a>
          </div>
          <div class="w-col w-col-2 w-col-small-2 w-col-tiny-2">
            <a class="industry process-link-block w-inline-block" href="#industry-research"></a>
          </div>
          <div class="w-col w-col-2 w-col-small-2 w-col-tiny-2">
            <a class="ideation process-link-block w-inline-block" href="#ideation"></a>
          </div>
