        <div class="w-richtext">
          <h4>Results&nbsp;</h4>
          <p>Before the course roadmap and lesson pages were sterile, with no opportunities for engagement. We changed that by introducing a clear progressive roadmap, bite-sized lessons, and interactive quizzes throughout the lesson. See details for before and after below. Click through for larger images.</p>
        </div>
        <a class="w-inline-block w-lightbox" href="#"><img class="project-body-image" src="../images/Canopy Before anotated.png" width="80%">
          <script class="w-json" type="application/json">
