        <div class="w-richtext">
          <p>With our final iteration complete for mobile, we created mock-ups for these pages into desktop format. Click through for larger images.</p>
        </div>
        <a class="w-inline-block w-lightbox" href="#"><img class="project-body-image" src="../images/Screen Shot 2016-06-13 at 4.17.22 PM.png" width="80%">
